text:
You're punctual.
Would you like something to drink?

No, I'm fine.
Thank you for letting me use the rehearsal room until late.
Alright, I'll return the key then.

Well, from our perspective...
we also want you to rest properly.

Especially now that the performance is coming up,
we want you to take care of yourself, or rather...

......Thank you.
But, I don't want to have any regrets.
I want to do everything I can.

But...
Are you feeling any burden?

You know...
The performance has changed a bit, hasn't it?

Are you saying that dancing contemporary alone
might be a burden?

If that's the case, don't worry. I'll always
deliver the best performance as usual.

I'm looking forward to it.
SHHis's... performance.
